    <note type="dates"><date>1829–1903</date></note>
    <sex value="M"/>
    <note type="biography">
        <p>Brewer and naturalist. Younger brother of Henry Walter Bates. Managing director of a brewing company in Leicester. A keen entomologist, particularly interested in the Heteromera, publishing many papers and forming an extensive collection. Also formed collections of tiger beetles and British Coleoptera. Cultivated orchids for some years.</p></note>
